<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 p-3 md:p-6 transition-colors duration-300"
     data-controller="exercise-checker text-toggle font-controls"
     data-text-toggle-target="content"
     data-font-controls-target="content">

  <%= render 'shared/page_header', pagina: @pagina %>

  <div class="space-y-6">

    <!-- Sezione teoria -->
    <div class="p-4 md:p-6">
      <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-4">
        Le misure di massa si usano per pesare oggetti molto pesanti (treni, navi...), ma anche per pesare oggetti molto piccoli, come i medicinali.
      </p>

      <div class="p-3 bg-pink-light dark:bg-pink-900/40 rounded-xl w-fit mb-6">
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
          L'unità di misura fondamentale della <strong>massa</strong> è il <strong>chilogrammo</strong> (<strong class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-600 dark:text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-400 border-b-2 border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">kg</strong>).
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Tabella MULTIPLI - UNITÀ - SOTTOMULTIPLI -->
      <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-6">
        <table class="w-full border-collapse border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600">
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th colspan="3" class="p-2 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 text-white font-bold">MULTIPLI</th>
              <th class="p-2 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 bg-cyan-500 text-white font-bold">UNITÀ FONDAMENTALE</th>
              <th colspan="3" class="p-2 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 bg-green-500 text-white font-bold">SOTTOMULTIPLI</th>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <th class="p-2 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 bg-cyan-50 dark:bg-cyan-900/50 text-center font-bold text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-600 dark:text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-400">Mg</th>
              <th class="p-2 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 bg-cyan-50 dark:bg-cyan-900/50 text-center text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400"></th>
              <th class="p-2 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 bg-cyan-50 dark:bg-cyan-900/50 text-center text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400"></th>
              <th class="p-2 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 bg-cyan-100 dark:bg-cyan-900 text-center font-bold text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-600 dark:text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-400">kg</th>
              <th class="p-2 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 bg-cyan-50 dark:bg-cyan-900/50 text-center font-bold text-green-600 dark:text-green-400">hg</th>
              <th class="p-2 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 bg-cyan-50 dark:bg-cyan-900/50 text-center font-bold text-green-600 dark:text-green-400">dag</th>
              <th class="p-2 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 bg-cyan-50 dark:bg-cyan-900/50 text-center font-bold text-green-600 dark:text-green-400">g</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td class="p-2 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 text-center text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">megagrammo</td>
              <td class="p-2 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 text-center text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">centinaio di kg</td>
              <td class="p-2 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 text-center text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">decina di kg</td>
              <td class="p-2 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 text-center text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">chilogrammo</td>
              <td class="p-2 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 text-center text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">ettogrammo</td>
              <td class="p-2 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 text-center text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">decagrammo</td>
              <td class="p-2 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 text-center text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">grammo</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="p-2 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 text-center text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="whitespace-nowrap">1 000</span> kg</td>
              <td class="p-2 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 text-center text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">100 kg</td>
              <td class="p-2 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 text-center text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">10 kg</td>
              <td class="p-2 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 text-center text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">1 kg</td>
              <td class="p-2 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 text-center text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">0,1 kg</td>
              <td class="p-2 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 text-center text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">0,01 kg</td>
              <td class="p-2 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 text-center text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">0,001 kg</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Sezione Massa e peso -->
    <div class="p-4 md:p-6">
      <h2 class="font-bold italic text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-600 dark:text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-400 mb-4">Massa e peso</h2>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-4">
            Massa e peso sono in realtà grandezze diverse (lo capirai l'anno prossimo studiando le Scienze), ma nella vita quotidiana la differenza non si nota e i due termini sono usati come sinonimi.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Tabella sottomultipli del grammo -->
        <div>
          <div class="overflow-x-auto">
            <table class="w-full border-collapse border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600">
              <thead>
                <tr>
                  <th colspan="4" class="p-2 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 bg-green-500 text-white font-bold">SOTTOMULTIPLI DEL GRAMMO</th>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <th class="p-2 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 bg-cyan-50 dark:bg-cyan-900/50 text-center font-bold text-green-600 dark:text-green-400">g</th>
                  <th class="p-2 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 bg-cyan-50 dark:bg-cyan-900/50 text-center font-bold text-green-600 dark:text-green-400">dg</th>
                  <th class="p-2 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 bg-cyan-50 dark:bg-cyan-900/50 text-center font-bold text-green-600 dark:text-green-400">cg</th>
                  <th class="p-2 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 bg-cyan-50 dark:bg-cyan-900/50 text-center font-bold text-green-600 dark:text-green-400">mg</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr>
                  <td class="p-2 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 text-center text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">grammo</td>
                  <td class="p-2 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 text-center text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">decigrammo</td>
                  <td class="p-2 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 text-center text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">centigrammo</td>
                  <td class="p-2 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 text-center text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">milligrammo</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td class="p-2 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 text-center text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">1 g</td>
                  <td class="p-2 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 text-center text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">0,1 g</td>
                  <td class="p-2 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 text-center text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">0,01 g</td>
                  <td class="p-2 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 text-center text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">0,001 g</td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Container esercizi -->
    <div class="p-4 md:p-6 bg-orange-100 dark:bg-orange-900/30 rounded-2xl">

      <!-- Box IMPARARE TUTTI -->
      <div class="p-4 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl -mx-4 md:-mx-6 -mt-4 md:-mt-6 mb-6 border-3 border-blue-500">
        <p class="font-bold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-4">
          <%= imparare_tutti_badge(1) %>
          Segna con una <span class="border-b-2 border-gray-700 dark:border-gray-300">X</span> le equivalenze corrette.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
            <input type="checkbox" class="w-5 h-5" data-correct-answer="true">
            <span>51,8 dg = 5,18 g</span>
          </label>
          <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
            <input type="checkbox" class="w-5 h-5" data-correct-answer="false">
            <span>70 g = 700 dag</span>
          </label>
          <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
            <input type="checkbox" class="w-5 h-5" data-correct-answer="false">
            <span>8 kg = 800 g</span>
          </label>
          <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
            <input type="checkbox" class="w-5 h-5" data-correct-answer="false">
            <span>905 mg = 90,5 dg</span>
          </label>
          <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
            <input type="checkbox" class="w-5 h-5" data-correct-answer="true">
            <span><span class="whitespace-nowrap">4 000</span> cg = 40 dag</span>
          </label>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <%= render 'shared/quaderno_link', pagine: [224, 225, 227, 234] %>

    <%= render 'shared/exercise_controls' %>
  </div>
</div>
